dc_title_s: A new map of Arabia divided into its several regions and districts from Mon D.Anville, geographer to the most Christian king with additions and improvements from Mr. Niebuhr.
dc_description_s: 1 map: col.; 18 X 20 1/2 in. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
